      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/kernel-ker-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "这些被彻底压扁的方向，合起来就叫做核，也就是零空间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "image",
      "line_id": "img-1",
