      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/image-img-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "再看输出：所有结果向量铺成的集合，就是像，也叫列空间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "image",
      "line_id": "img-2",
