      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/image-img-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.8,
      "size": 44784,
      "text": "满秩时像铺满整个平面，降一秩就塌成一条直线，全零则只剩原点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
