      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/theorem-thm-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "奇妙的是，它俩相加永远等于输入空间的维数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "thm-3",
      "filename": "theorem-thm-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kernel-image/theorem-thm-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "在平面里就是：秩加零化度恒等于二，一分不多一分不少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kernel-image",
      "section_id": "interaction",
